<item>
            <title>[LU-17465] Change default nodemap squash_uid/squash_gid to 65534</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17465</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Default values for nodemap.squash_uid/gid/projid are currently set to 99, to match user &apos;nobody&apos;. But on newer systems, nobody has changed to 65534 and 99 no longer exists.&lt;br/&gt;
It is safe to use 65534 in all cases, as even on older systems it exists and corresponds to &apos;nfsnobody&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
